creator: Triad Bank
descriptionHtml:
Mobile Banking allows you to check account balances, view transactions, transfer funds, and check messages. It is a free service available to Triad Bank, N.A. online banking customers.

Take charge of your finances on-the-go. You can:
-Check Balances
-View pending items and history
-Search history by date and description
-View, approve, or cancel all transactions
-Create funds transfers
-Create Single ACH/Domestic Wires from existing templates
-View and create secure messages

To use this application, you need to enroll in our mobile services via Online Banking.
descriptionShort: Take charge of your finances on-the-go, for free!
